PrecisAppointment of the Hon. WILLIAM L. HOYT, Chief Justice of New Brunswick, as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of NEW BRUNSWICK, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter, effective July 1, 1994.
